      Invert Z Axis: false
      Name: Current View
      Near Clip Distance: 0.009999999776482582
      Pitch: 0.530398428440094
      Target Frame: pascal/base_link
      Value: Orbit (rviz_default_plugins)
      Yaw: 0.6253974437713623
    Saved: ~
